sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Claude as Claude Code
    participant Hooks as Hook Engine
    participant Memory as CognitiveMemory
    participant Kuzu as Kuzu DB
    participant XPIA as XPIA Defender

    Note over Claude: Session starts
    Claude->>Hooks: SessionStart event
    Hooks->>Memory: initialize memory
    Memory->>Kuzu: retrieve relevant memories
    Kuzu-->>Memory: past discoveries, patterns
    Memory-->>Hooks: context enriched

    User->>Claude: types a prompt
    Claude->>Hooks: UserPromptSubmit
    Hooks->>Hooks: workflow classification
    Hooks-->>Claude: (optionally modified prompt)

    Claude->>Claude: processes prompt, calls tool
    Claude->>Hooks: PreToolUse(tool_name, input)
    Hooks->>XPIA: scan for prompt injection
    XPIA-->>Hooks: allow/deny
    Hooks-->>Claude: decision

    Claude->>Claude: tool executes
    Claude->>Hooks: PostToolUse(tool_name, result)
    Hooks->>XPIA: scan result for threats
    XPIA-->>Hooks: clean

    Note over Claude: Context window filling up
    Claude->>Hooks: PreCompact
    Hooks->>Hooks: save critical context

    Note over Claude: Session ending
    Claude->>Hooks: Stop event
    Hooks->>Memory: store session discoveries
    Memory->>Kuzu: persist to graph DB
    Hooks->>Hooks: reflection & cleanup
    Hooks-->>Claude: session complete
